=Analyze this lead submission and provide a comprehensive qualification analysis. Use the provided form data, website scrape, and email verification results to provide the most accurate insights.

Name: {{$json.name}}
Email: {{$json.email}}
Company: {{$json.company}}
Interest: {{$json.interest}}
Message: {{$json.message}}
Budget: {{$json.budget}}

Website Scraped Data:
- Website Legitimacy Status: {{$json.isLegit}}
- Website Legitimacy Score: {{$json.legitScore}}
- Website Markdown Content: {{$json.scrapedData.markdown}}
- Website Metadata: {{$json.scrapedData.metadata.title}} | {{$json.scrapedData.metadata.description}}

Email Verification Data:
- Hunter.io Status: {{$json.hunterData.status}}
- Hunter.io Score: {{$json.hunterData.score}}
- Hunter.io is Webmail: {{$json.hunterData.webmail}}
- Hunter.io is Disposable: {{$json.hunterData.disposable}}

Combined Lead Score (from all sources): {{$json.leadScore}}

Based on all the above data, provide a JSON response with:
1. sentiment: positive/neutral/negative
2. intent: sales/support/information/spam
3. qualification: hot/warm/cold/spam
4. urgency: high/medium/low
5. summary: brief analysis (max 100 chars)
6. suggestedTags: array of relevant tags (e.g., ["real-estate", "ai-automation", "high-ticket"])
7. adjustedScore: number 0-100 (this should be the same as the final combined lead score)

Response format: {"sentiment": "positive", "intent": "sales", "qualification": "hot", "urgency": "high", "summary": "High-value prospect with clear project needs", "suggestedTags": ["web-dev", "e-commerce", "high-budget"], "adjustedScore": 85}

